  "notes": "The optionality of the MPAN Address and MAP contract details will be determined by the MAP in the bilateral agreement between the MAP and MOP or the agreement between the MAP and the Supplier as appropriate in the circumstances.In addition to the mandatory scenarios when this flow must be sent, it may also be used by bilateral agreement when the MPAN Address and / or MAP contract details have changed."
